include ../bem/index
include ../helpers/config
+b.SECTION.testimonial#section-testimonial
	+e.shape._right.shape__._brand-1._transparent(data-emergence="hidden")
		+e.inner
			+e.inner-shape._brand-1
	+e.container.container
		+e.row.vrow
			.vcol-12.vcol-sm-6.vcol-md-7
				+b.vtitle-group
					+e.H3.title.vtitle-lg Customer Testimonials
					+e.content
						+b.P.title-md
							| Customers are always happy. They know that 
							+b.SPAN.highlight Vsevolod Kurochka 
							| is the key to success and quality. Here are some confirmations to this.
			.vcol-12.vcol-sm-6.vcol-md-5
				+e.items-wrapper
					+e.item
						+e.item-header
							+e.item-image-wrapper
								+e.item-image(src="img/testimonial/item1.jpg")
						+e.item-body
							+e.item-body-content
								p Man is the word! He said he did. It's nice to work, I advise everyone.
						+e.item-footer
							+e.P.item-title Dmitry Kirpach
							+e.P.item-subtitle CEO&amp;Founder
	+e.P.letters-bg.letters-bg(data-emergence="hidden") The Best